  "description": "Position advancing forward at 0.003 per second while LFO2 simultaneously sweeps backward through position scatter — the buffer playhead slowly advances while grains are harvested from random points around it. At 300ms Gaussian grains and density=14, the granulator occupies multiple temporal positions simultaneously. pitchShift=-5 semitones plus pitchScatter=8 semitones means grains arrive across a 19-semitone band. Time is not a line — it is a probability distribution.",
